data.description: Assumable Mortgage! Peace and quiet is what you'll find in this hidden gem. This floor plan allows for so many options, whether you're looking for office space, room for a home gym or an extra dining room, this home has it all! 3 generously sized bedrooms up, with primary suite. All the living space you'll need on the main, and the yard is just wow! Grow your own veggies and fruit or gather at the firepit for s'mores and stories. RV parking and NO HOA!  Garage has been converted to living space.
